{
  "stem": "26728.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And think it was French, but I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The rabbi spoke, you know, several languages.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was-- thank God for him, because I learned more about what this Holocaust business was about in the first instance, by listening to him explain how the structure of the camp was, how the infrastructure, how they were treated by the SS, how some of the-- how they protected each other from the bad guys, the kapos.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Uh, there were criminals in there, who-- very cruel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were ordered to whip each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were-- there were men who would refuse to do that, barracks leaders, who of course, were in some cases beaten to death.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in some cases, the SS just ignored them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he told us those kind of stories.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Uh, and-- and we met with him a couple of times.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we'd sit around, like I said, smoking cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The guy couldn't get enough cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There wasn't a-- there wasn't any place in there that was sanitary, anywhere.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Except in the-- in the SS, uh, sect-- the SS, uh, section of the camp, where the commandant and his-- his men lived.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is, remember, the Bitch of Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now the commandant, uh, Els-- her name was Elsie, Ilsa, I have it over there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was, uh, tried.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She's the one that had the lampshades.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This-- after-- one of the times-- after I had seen the crematoriums and the bodies, stacked bodies, and, uh, wandered-- driven around the camp, and had to walk in someplace where you couldn't drive.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This guy said, you gotta see this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember him saying that to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He said, this is unreal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know what the hell this is all about.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
